"""
RHD Analyzer - ISBT-Informed RHD Analysis
Uses identity-based classification with SNP detection for major ISBT alleles.
Note: This is a simplified implementation based on published ISBT standards.
For complete allele classification, consult blooddatabase.isbtweb.org
"""

